\subsection{Threat Hunting Workflow in Kibana}
\begin{enumerate}
 \item Observe a high-severity alert on the main Kibana dashboard.
 \item Click the source IP to filter all dashboard visualizations to that
host.
 \item Pivot to the DNS visualization to review all domain queries made
immediately before and after the alert.
 \item Examine the TLS visualization for malicious certificate details.
 \item Use the \texttt{flow\_id} to reconstruct the full attack sequence: TCP
connection $\rightarrow$ DNS query $\rightarrow$ TLS handshake $\rightarrow$
alert $\rightarrow$ data transfer.
\end{enumerate}

