and want to protect (e.g.\ \texttt{192.168.0.0/16, 10.0.0.0/8}). & \textbf{Yes ---
the main setting} \\ \hline
\texttt{EXTERNAL\_NET} & Everything that is \emph{not} \texttt{HOME\_NET}; usually
